
## Euclidean Algorithm

```txt
EUCLID(a,b)
  if b = 0
    then return a
  else return EUCLID(b, a mod b)
```

```txt
EUCLID(a,b)
  while b not equal 0
    h <- a mod b
    a <- b
    b <- h
  return a
```

